Dialogs.Dialog: Can I stay by your side？
Don't move... I'm going to get closer to you.
Hehe, what's wrong？ You face is getting red.
Hey, don't you want us to get closer？
I can feel your body temperature...
I'll get closer to you just a little bit, okay？
Is there something sticking on my face？
Hehe... What do you intend to do？
Hehehe. Do you like me that much？
Not yet... This is getting awkward.
Don't be nervous, okay？ Just relax.
I'm so happy when you take charge like this...
You can come closer to me...
Hehe, are you okay？ Can you do it？
I'm not going to refuse, so don't worry.
You can come closer to me. I don't mind.
I don't mind if you want to touch me...
I want you to touch me more...
I don't think this is good...
I'm not in the mood for this...
Hey... I was really in the mood...
I wanted to get closer to you, but...
No~！ We are not ready for this, okay？
This is still quite awkward. Maybe we should consider the mood.
Not now. Maybe we can do this later.
No！ Hehe. I was teasing you.
A little bit more might be good, right？
Hehe, this is still not enough.
Hehe, now I've become like this.
Stay by my side forever, okay？
Don't look at me like that...
It's embarrassing... Don't look at me.
Phew... Somehow, I feel relieved now...
Some more... would be nice, right？
Let us be like this forever.
You want to do this again？
You should be gentle to a girl, you know？
Are you going to kiss me？
I don't mind if you do it.
Are you trying to hold it？
We are thinking about the same thing, aren't we？
You know what to do, right？
Please... Once more. That's okay, right？
I like this more and more...
Hey, one more time... I beg you.
Do it one more time. Okay？
Hey, this is not enough, right？
More... I want to feel you more...
Come closer... Hey, it's okay, right？
I feel as if my heart is going to burst out...
It feels like my heart has been filled up.
Do you feel like the distance between us has become shorter...？
More... I want to know you more...
I'm too happy that I feel scared... What will you do then？
You will be by my side forever, right？
My heart is throbbing. Can you hear it？
I love you. Hehe, you know it, right？
We will never be apart, right？
You can keep doing this, okay？
Will it be more than this next time...？
It's embarrassing, but at the same time, I'm happy.
I really feel satisfied. Thanks to you.
Phew... Somehow, this makes me feel dizzy.
I like this... I wonder how long we can keep doing this...
I feel like I'm madly in love with you now.
I'm in tears again. This is weird, huh？
You will always be by my side, right？
I feel like I've become one with you. Such a relieving feeling...
I'll have some expectation from now on...
You know the right timing, huh？
There are things that you like but I don't.
We should hold on to the fun moment, okay？
Today is not good... Maybe later.
Don't rush it. We should take it slowly, right？
Well... It's better if we take some more time...
It's such a bad timing for today.
You have to consider it more, okay？
Hmm... My body has gone numb...
I feel so warm like this.
I hope we can kiss like this again.
I want to keep you to myself.
I can't say a word now... I'm so happy that I'm going to cry.
I won't allow you to stay away from me even for a moment▼
We do this so often but why do I feel very happy like this today？
I want to know more about you. I will also tell you everything about myself...
Everything in my head turns blank now... I love you. I really love you.
You will never leave me... Never ever going to leave me, right？
No... If you do this, I won't be able to stay away from you. Is that okay？
Hey, I don't want you to ever leave me...
Now, I can't take my eyes off of you... It's your fault...
I feel like I'm the luckiest person in the world. Of course, that's because of what you did.
Hey, can't you sense my body language？ You're so crafty. You made me become like this.
You really enjoy doing this, huh...？
